{
  "stem": "18186.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 253.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Do you know how to write in Jewish?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I think I still remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because I had a tutor at home, and we were-- we were very Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So they gave me a pencil.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there was a window sill, with no window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they told me what to write.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that what's made them-- Believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--believe that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because with no other people-- Polish, Ukrainian-- knew how to write Yiddish, Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So those three men at that time also returned from the war as survivors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, that's my husband-- one of them, my husband knew him very well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One name was [NON-ENGLISH], like I don't remember the first name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other one was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I said, the Polish name, I forgot-- the German guy, you asked me the German's second name, and I don't remember if it was-- it was [NON-ENGLISH] or was-- anyway, that name from the Jewish guy was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the third one, I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was so-- so-- so, they took us into their place, they had a little tiny room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we never get to the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were so excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they had-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and they said, so what do you want to do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I would like to be with Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said to me, we are getting ready to go further-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't want to stay here in Poland, because they don't like us here anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we'll go from Germany, and maybe from Germany we'll go to United States, or maybe to Israel, wherever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Israel wasn't Israel yet then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Palestine, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's what we planning to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
